#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn22.123"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn22.123:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 22 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 22 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.123:0.2"
msgid "12. Dhammakathikavagga "
msgstr "12. A Dhamma speaker "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: 123. Sutavantasutta → sutavā (pts1)
msgctxt "sn22.123:0.3"
msgid "123. Sutavantasutta "
msgstr "123. Educated "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn22.123:1.1"
msgid "Ekaṃ samayaṃ āyasmā ca sāriputto āyasmā ca mahākoṭṭhiko bārāṇasiyaṃ viharanti isipatane migadāye. "
msgstr "At one time Venerable Sāriputta and Venerable Mahākoṭṭhita were staying near Benares, in the deer park at Isipatana. "

msgctxt "sn22.123:1.2"
msgid "Atha kho āyasmā mahākoṭṭhiko sāyanhasamayaṃ paṭisallānā vuṭṭhito yenāyasmā sāriputto tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā … pe … etadavoca: "
msgstr "Then in the late afternoon, Venerable Mahākoṭṭhita came out of retreat, went to Venerable Sāriputta, bowed, sat down to one side, and said: "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "sn22.123:2.1"
msgid "“Sutavatāvuso sāriputta, bhikkhunā katame dhammā yoniso manasi kātabbā”ti? "
msgstr "“Reverend Sāriputta, what things should an educated mendicant properly attend to?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.123:2.2"
msgid "“Sutavatāvuso koṭṭhika, bhikkhunā pañcupādānakkhandhā aniccato … pe … anattato yoniso manasi kātabbā. "
msgstr "“An educated mendicant should properly attend to these five grasping aggregates as impermanent … as not-self. "

msgctxt "sn22.123:2.3"
msgid "Katame pañca? "
msgstr "What five? "

msgctxt "sn22.123:2.4"
msgid "Seyyathidaṃ—rūpupādānakkhandho … pe … viññāṇupādānakkhandho. "
msgstr "That is, the grasping aggregates of form, feeling, perception, choices, and consciousness. "

msgctxt "sn22.123:2.5"
msgid "Sutavatāvuso koṭṭhika, bhikkhunā ime pañcupādānakkhandhā aniccato … pe … anattato yoniso manasi kātabbā. "
msgstr "An educated mendicant should properly attend to these five grasping aggregates as impermanent … as not-self. "

msgctxt "sn22.123:2.6"
msgid "Ṭhānaṃ kho panetaṃ, āvuso, vijjati—yaṃ sutavā bhikkhu ime pañcupādānakkhandhe aniccato … pe … anattato yoniso manasi karonto sotāpattiphalaṃ sacchikareyyā”ti. "
msgstr "It’s possible that an educated mendicant who regards the five grasping aggregates in this way will realize the fruit of stream-entry.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "sn22.123:3.1"
msgid "“Sotāpannena panāvuso sāriputta, bhikkhunā katame dhammā yoniso manasi kātabbā”ti? "
msgstr "“But Reverend Sāriputta, what things should a mendicant stream-enterer properly attend to?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.123:3.2"
msgid "“Sotāpannenapi kho āvuso koṭṭhika, bhikkhunā ime pañcupādānakkhandhā aniccato … pe … anattato yoniso manasi kātabbā. "
msgstr "“A mendicant stream-enterer should properly attend to these five grasping aggregates as impermanent … as not-self. "

msgctxt "sn22.123:3.3"
msgid "Ṭhānaṃ kho panetaṃ, āvuso, vijjati—yaṃ sotāpanno bhikkhu ime pañcupādānakkhandhe aniccato … pe … anattato yoniso manasi karonto sakadāgāmiphalaṃ … pe … "
msgstr "It’s possible that a mendicant stream-enterer who regards the five grasping aggregates in this way will realize the fruit of once-return.” … "

msgctxt "sn22.123:3.4"
msgid "anāgāmiphalaṃ … pe … "
msgstr "“It’s possible that a mendicant once-returner who regards the five grasping aggregates in this way will realize the fruit of non-return.” … "

msgctxt "sn22.123:3.5"
msgid "arahattaphalaṃ sacchikareyyā”ti. "
msgstr "“It’s possible that a mendicant non-returner who regards the five grasping aggregates in this way will realize the fruit of perfection.” … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc4
msgctxt "sn22.123:4.1"
msgid "“Arahatā panāvuso sāriputta, katame dhammā yoniso manasi kātabbā”ti? "
msgstr "“But Reverend Sāriputta, what things should a perfected one properly attend to?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.123:4.2"
msgid "“Arahatāpi khvāvuso koṭṭhika, ime pañcupādānakkhandhā aniccato dukkhato rogato gaṇḍato sallato aghato ābādhato parato palokato suññato anattato yoniso manasi kātabbā. "
msgstr "“Reverend Koṭṭhita, a perfected one should properly attend to the five grasping aggregates as impermanent, as suffering, as diseased, as an abscess, as a dart, as misery, as an affliction, as alien, as falling apart, as empty, as not-self. "

msgctxt "sn22.123:4.3"
msgid "Natthi, khvāvuso, arahato uttari karaṇīyaṃ, katassa vā paticayo; "
msgstr "A perfected one has nothing more to do, and nothing that needs improvement. "

msgctxt "sn22.123:4.4"
msgid "api ca kho ime dhammā bhāvitā bahulīkatā diṭṭhadhammasukhavihārāya ceva saṃvattanti satisampajaññāya cā”ti. "
msgstr "Still, these things, when developed and cultivated, lead to blissful meditation in the present life, and also to mindfulness and situational awareness.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn22.123:4.5"
msgid "Ekādasamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

